-- Bertelsmann Sells Half of Pubbles Stake, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 2012-01-04T06:21:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/bertelsmann-sells-half-of-pubbles-stake-handelsblatt-reports.html
Bertelsmann AG (BTG)  has sold half of the
Internet platform Pubbles that markets magazines, newspapers and
books to publisher Verlagsgruppe Weltbild GmbH,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ragnhild Kjetland in Frankfurt at 
 rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  